# Refresh-state singleton — written by RefreshStore on every transition
# (start / advance / complete / fail) under fcntl.flock. Carries the
# in-flight refresh's started_utc / current_stage / finished_utc / source
# / last_error. Cross-thread + cross-tab + cross-container-restart, but
# scoped to one deployment; never shipped in git.
data/refresh_status.json

# Personal scratch / backlog — see CLAUDE.md (eventually) for content.
NOTES.md
